These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, tea, almond-milk, coffee
Sport: climbing, baseball, volleyball, lacrosse
1. Beverage:mirinda is on the right of Sport:volleyball##1
2. Sport:lacrosse is on the far left##1
3. Sport:volleyball is between Sport:baseball and Beverage:tea##2
4. Beverage:coffee is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:almond-milk is between Beverage:tea and Beverage:mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee         | tea   | almond-milk | mirinda       |
| Sport      | lacrosse | climbing | volleyball   | baseball |

