3. Nationality:pakistani is on the right of Nationality:brazilian##1
4. Hobby:photography is on the left of Nationality:brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | writing | photography | singing | camping |
| Nationality   | spanish    | american   | brazilian | pakistani       |

